        <item>
            <title>空中的士 Volocopter 申請破產保護，曾獲 Mercedes-Benz 和吉利汽車注資</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/01/volocopter-files-for-bankruptcy/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=volocopter-files-for-bankruptcy</link>
